title: Bug 109350 - Output parameter not displaying in data set dialog.
OB: The output parameter is not displayed in the edit data set dialog.
EB: The output parameter should be displayed in the edit data set dialog.
SR:
To reproduce the issue:
1. Call the stored procedure from the Oracle database.
2. Check the query result in the edit data set dialog.

Expected result:
The output parameter should be visible in the edit data set dialog.
